projectGridLines.title: Title: Full Stack Development Intern
projectGridLines.description:
Title: Full Stack Development Intern


Description: MarianaAI has a small tech team, driven by folks who have previously

built India’s largest AI Model and one of the world’s only real-time RecSys engines.

As we build deeper features and added modules for the MarianaAI platform, the role

of a Full-Stack Development intern shall be to work closely with the tech team to

build products that deliver an exceptional AI-native experience at scale. The role

focuses on front-end and back-end development across our Web, iOS, and Android

Apps and can also entail collaborating with the MarianaAI team on MLOps as well

building and deploying SOTA AI Models.

Skill sets: GoLang, React, Python

Traits expectation: Previously built some internship

Expected learning:

Specific courses required for project execution: CSE
